<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>甘南·九寨沟 自驾之旅</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: #eef4ee;
            background-image: linear-gradient(145deg, #e2ece2 0%, #f6faf6 100%);
            color: #1e3a2e;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* 头部 */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a61c1c 0%, #c41a1a 70%, #b31b1b 100%);
            color: #f9e8b4;
            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(160, 40, 40, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header::after {
            content: "✦ ✦ ✦";
            font-size: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            opacity: 0.2;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            right: 20px;
            color: #f9e8b4;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .header .sub {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 8px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }

        .header .meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: rgba(255, 215, 140, 0.15);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 140, 0.2);
        }

        .header .meta span {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .header .meta i {
            color: #f5c518;
        }

        /* 总览卡片 */
        .summary {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: -15px 0 30px;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .summary-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 18px 12px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 20, 10, 0.08);
            border-left: 6px solid #c41a1a;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .summary-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 20, 10, 0.12);
        }

        .summary-card i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #c41a1a;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .summary-card .num {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e3a2e;
        }

        .summary-card .label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #4a5f4a;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* 时间线 */
        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .day-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 20, 10, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #dce8dc;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .day-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 20, 10, 0.12);
        }

        .day-header {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px 24px;
            padding: 18px 24px;
            background: #f4faf4;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dce8dc;
            cursor: default;
        }

        .day-header .day-badge {
            background: #c41a1a;
            color: #f9e8b4;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .day-header .date {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a2e;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .day-header .route {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2d5a2d;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .day-header .route i {
            color: #c41a1a;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .day-header .route .arrow {
            color: #b8860b;
        }

        .day-body {
            padding: 20px 24px 24px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 18px 30px;
        }

        .day-body .item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .day-body .item .label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #6a7f6a;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .day-body .item .label i {
            width: 18px;
            color: #c41a1a;
        }

        .day-body .item .value {
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1e3a2e;
            padding-left: 26px;
        }

        .day-body .item .value .highlight {
            background: #fcf3d4;
            padding: 0 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .day-body .full-width {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .day-body .cost-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px 24px;
            padding-left: 26px;
        }

        .day-body .cost-grid span {
            background: #f2f8f2;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border: 1px solid #d4e2d4;
        }

        .day-body .cost-grid i {
            color: #c41a1a;
            margin-right: 4px;
        }

        /* 景点特殊标记 */
        .must-see {
            background: #fcf3d4;
            border-left: 4px solid #f5c518;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* 底栏 */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #4a5f4a;
            border-top: 2px dashed #c0d4c0;
            padding-top: 30px;
            background: #f4faf4;
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer i {
            color: #c41a1a;
        }

        /* 响应式 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .day-body {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .day-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 8px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .summary {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            .day-body .cost-grid {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 6px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .header .meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 6px;
            }
            .summary {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .day-body {
                padding: 14px 16px;
            }
            .day-header {
                padding: 14px 16px;
            }
        }

        .prayer-flags {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4px;
            margin: 6px 0 0;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        .prayer-flags span {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 32px;
            background: #f5c518;
            clip-path: polygon(0% 0%, 100% 0%, 80% 100%, 20% 100%);
            animation: flap 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        .prayer-flags span:nth-child(2) {
            background: #c41a1a;
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }
        .prayer-flags span:nth-child(3) {
            background: #4a90d9;
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }
        .prayer-flags span:nth-child(4) {
            background: #1e7a5e;
            animation-delay: 0.9s;
        }
        .prayer-flags span:nth-child(5) {
            background: #f5c518;
            animation-delay: 1.2s;
        }

        @keyframes flap {
            0% {
                transform: skewX(-3deg) scaleY(1);
            }
            100% {
                transform: skewX(3deg) scaleY(1.05);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- 头部 -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🏔️ 甘南 · 九寨沟</h1>
            <div class="sub">秘境自驾 · 9日沉浸之旅</div>
            <div class="prayer-flags">
                <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> 7月 · 9天8晚</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 成都租车 · 兰州还车</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-route"></i> 约1400 km</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-users"></i> 与父母同行</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 总览卡片 -->
        <div class="summary">
            <div class="summary-card"><i class="fas fa-map-pin"></i><div class="num">9</div><div class="label">游玩日</div></div>
            <div class="summary-card"><i class="fas fa-mountain"></i><div class="num">12+</div><div class="label">核心景点</div></div>
            <div class="summary-card"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i><div class="num">~5h</div><div class="label">日均车程</div></div>
            <div class="summary-card"><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i><div class="num">~¥540</div><div class="label">门票/人</div></div>
            <div class="summary-card"><i class="fas fa-bed"></i><div class="num">8</div><div class="label">住宿晚数</div></div>
        </div>

        <!-- 行程时间线 -->
        <div class="timeline">

            <!-- Day 1：抵达成都 → 取车 → 游玩成都 → 夜宿广汉（三星堆） -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 1</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X日 · 星期X</span>
                    <div class="route"><i class="fas fa-plane-arrival"></i> 各地 → 成都 <span class="arrow">⟶</span> <i class="fas fa-museum"></i> 广汉·三星堆</div>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-train"></i> 交通</span><div class="value">高铁抵达成都</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 租车</span><div class="value">办理SUV租车手续</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> 游玩攻略</span><div class="value">
                        • 下午游览 <span class="highlight">宽窄巷子</span> 或 <span class="highlight">锦里</span>，品尝成都小吃。<br>
                        • 傍晚从成都出发，自驾前往广汉市（约1-1.5小时，G5京昆高速），<strong>夜宿三星堆附近酒店</strong>。
                    </div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i> 住宿</span><div class="value">广汉市（三星堆附近）</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 费用</span><div class="value"><span class="cost-grid"><span><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> 油费 ￥40</span><span><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路费 ￥20</span><span><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> 门票 —</span></span></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 2：三星堆游览 → 下午出发前往九寨沟 -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 2</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X+1日 · 星期X</span>
                    <div class="route"><i class="fas fa-museum"></i> 三星堆 <span class="arrow">⟶</span> <i class="fas fa-water"></i> 九寨沟</div>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 交通方式</span><div class="value">自驾 · 九环线东线</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 车程</span><div class="value">约380km · 6.5~7.5小时</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路况及路线</span><div class="value"><span class="highlight">广汉→绵阳→江油→平武→九寨沟</span>，后半段为盘山公路，谨慎驾驶。</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> 游玩攻略</span><div class="value">
                        <span class="must-see">⭐ 古蜀文明</span><br>
                        • <strong>上午 8:30</strong> 进入<span class="highlight">三星堆博物馆</span>游览（约3-4小时，门票¥72/人，需提前公众号预约）。<br>
                        • <strong>13:00前</strong> 出发前往九寨沟，预计晚上8-9点抵达沟口。<br>
                        • <strong>⚠️ 九寨沟门票需提前7-14天在官方渠道预约！</strong>
                    </div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i> 住宿</span><div class="value">九寨沟沟口</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 费用</span><div class="value"><span class="cost-grid"><span><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> 油费 ￥230</span><span><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路费 ￥180</span><span><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> 门票 ￥72/人</span></span></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 3：九寨沟全天 -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 3</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X+2日 · 星期X</span>
                    <div class="route"><i class="fas fa-tree"></i> 九寨沟全天游览</div>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-bus"></i> 交通方式</span><div class="value">景区观光车</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 游玩时长</span><div class="value">全天 · 约8小时</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> 游玩攻略</span><div class="value"><span class="must-see">⭐ 世界自然遗产</span><br>按“Y”字形路线：<br>• <strong>上午</strong> 则查洼沟（长海、五彩池）<br>• <strong>中午</strong> 日则沟（五花海、珍珠滩瀑布、镜海）<br>• <strong>下午</strong> 树正沟（树正群海、盆景滩）<br><span class="highlight">门票¥190 + 观光车¥90 = ¥280/人</span></div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i> 住宿</span><div class="value">九寨沟沟口</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 费用</span><div class="value"><span class="cost-grid"><span><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> 油费 —</span><span><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路费 —</span><span><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> 门票 ￥280/人</span></span></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 4：九寨沟 → 唐克 -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 4</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X+3日 · 星期X</span>
                    <div class="route"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> 九寨沟 → 唐克 <span class="arrow">⟶</span> <i class="fas fa-water"></i> 九曲黄河第一湾</div>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 交通方式</span><div class="value">自驾 · 九若路</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 车程</span><div class="value">约270km · 5~6小时</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路况及路线</span><div class="value"><span class="highlight">九若路</span>（九寨沟→若尔盖→唐克），盘山公路，海拔渐升至3000米以上。</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> 游玩攻略</span><div class="value">上午出发，下午抵达唐克，傍晚前往 <span class="highlight">九曲黄河第一湾</span> 观日落（门票+扶梯 ¥105/人）。</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i> 住宿</span><div class="value">唐克镇</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 费用</span><div class="value"><span class="cost-grid"><span><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> 油费 ￥160</span><span><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路费 ￥0</span><span><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> 门票 ￥105/人</span></span></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 5：唐克 → 郎木寺 -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 5</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X+4日 · 星期X</span>
                    <div class="route"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> 唐克 → 郎木寺 <span class="arrow">⟶</span> <i class="fas fa-church"></i> 郎木寺镇</div>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 交通方式</span><div class="value">自驾 · 248国道</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 车程</span><div class="value">约140km · 2~2.5小时</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路况及路线</span><div class="value">248国道，路况良好，穿行若尔盖草原。</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> 游玩攻略</span><div class="value">上午休整，中午出发，下午游览 <span class="highlight">四川格尔底寺</span>（¥30/人），感受“一镇跨两省”。</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i> 住宿</span><div class="value">郎木寺镇</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 费用</span><div class="value"><span class="cost-grid"><span><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> 油费 ￥85</span><span><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路费 ￥20</span><span><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> 门票 ￥30/人</span></span></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 6：郎木寺 → 扎尕那 -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 6</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X+5日 · 星期X</span>
                    <div class="route"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> 郎木寺 → 扎尕那 <span class="arrow">⟶</span> <i class="fas fa-mountain"></i> 扎尕那</div>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 交通方式</span><div class="value">自驾 · 248国道</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 车程</span><div class="value">约95km · 1.5~2小时</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路况及路线</span><div class="value">248国道，路况良好。</div></div>
                    <div class="item full-width"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> 游玩攻略</span><div class="value">上午游览 <span class="highlight">甘肃赛赤寺</span>（¥30/人），可去 <span class="highlight">纳摩大峡谷</span> 轻徒步。下午抵达扎尕那，入住民宿。</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i> 住宿</span><div class="value">扎尕那（达日/代巴村）</div></div>
                    <div class="item"><span class="label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 费用</span><div class="value"><span class="cost-grid"><span><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i> 油费 ￥55</span><span><i class="fas fa-road"></i> 路费 ￥10</span><span><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i> 门票 赛赤寺¥30 + 扎尕那¥80</span></span></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 7：扎尕那全天 -->
            <div class="day-card">
                <div class="day-header">
                    <span class="day-badge">Day 7</span>
                    <span class="date">7月X+6日 · 星期X</span>
